title: LYNDA MATHEMATICA 10 ADVANCED ANALYSIS TUTORIAL
description:
This training course teaches analysts how to go beyond the
basics of Mathematica 10 and start analyzing financial
data, applying machine-learning algorithms, predicting and
classifying data using linear and logistic regression, and
analyzing relationships on social networks. Author Curt
Frye also shows how to display maps, investigate data about
different countries and time periods, visualize random
data, and gain better insights from text. Using these
techniques, you'll have the power and flexibility you need
to dive deep into the information at hand and make good
decisions for your organization

Topics include:

* Generating maps

* Displaying statistical data about countries and cities

* Displaying changes in stock prices

* Calculating exchange rates

* Counting links in a social network

* Calculating reciprocity

* Applying machine-learning algorithms

* Analyzing text data
